  <li id="comment-10655" class="comment even thread-even depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="https://www.blogger.com/profile/10062142912057426459" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">Rich Terrell</a></cite></div>
